WEBVTT

00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:31.321
since the 1500s

00:09:31.321 --> 00:09:33.852
to establish what the precedents are.

00:09:33.852 --> 00:09:35.848
And in 11 out of 15 of them,

00:09:35.848 --> 00:09:37.915
let me tell you,

00:09:37.915 --> 00:09:41.050
they've ended in catastrophic war.

00:09:41.050 --> 00:09:44.486
You may say, "But Kevin --

00:09:44.486 --> 00:09:46.785
or Conqueror of the Classics --

00:09:46.785 --> 00:09:48.967
that was the past.

00:09:48.967 --> 00:09:52.102
We live now in a world
of interdependence and globalization.

00:09:52.102 --> 00:09:53.565
It could never happen again."

00:09:53.565 --> 00:09:54.911
Guess what?

00:09:54.911 --> 00:09:57.581
The economic historians
tell us that in fact,

00:09:57.581 --> 00:09:59.900
the time which we reached
the greatest point

00:09:59.900 --> 00:10:02.719
of economic integration and globalization